data.title: WHICH DO YOU WATCH LESS WPCH 17, WATL 36 OR WUPA 69 ?
data.meta_description:
I hardly ever watch anything on WPCH or WUPA. Sometimes I watch "Wheel" on WATL.
That's about it. I think they all 3 are sorry excuses for a tv station...
data.text:
Jan 15, 2012

#1

I hardly ever watch anything on WPCH or WUPA. Sometimes I watch "Wheel" on WATL.

That's about it. I think they all 3 are sorry excuses for a tv station.

But I do watch Antenna TV on 36.3 quite a bit.

Jan 15, 2012

#2

I watch reruns of the Simpsons and SouthPark on WATL and Family Guy, American Dad and My Name Is Earl on WPCH and that is it. I watch absolutely nothing on WUPA.

So I suppose I watch WUPA the least

Jan 15, 2012

#3

I least watch CW69/WUPA. Once UPN died a lot of African American shows were dropped from WUPA. I watch MyATL 36 sometimes when Im off during the daytime to laugh at Jerry Springer, Maury, Steve and Cheaters. Peachtree TV I only watch for In The Heat of The Night at 9am and Tyler Perry show.
